	&lt;li&gt;Hence, this meaning is best reflected by&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;option 4&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;making it the correct answer.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Philanderer&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

